	(text "J1: 60-pin (2x30) -- standard 8-bit ISA pinout off-board (S4.3); same as the soft-card IN/OUT headers (isa_conn). -5V/+-12V reclaimed for ~{IOCHCK}/IRQ8/GND."
		(at 139.7 106.68 0)
		(effects
